mo uses local model weights in DOS, plus visible files, tests, and logs.                                                                                                                  looped output loop control shorter prompt reset answer loops                                                                                                    Loop control                                                    Use a shorter prompt and reset if the answer loops.                                                                                                                                             checklist release check tag assets checksums tests                                                                                                              Release checklist                                               Check the tag, assets, checksums, and tests.                                                                                                                                                    offline limit dos cannot browse answer comes local files                                                                                                        Offline limit                                                   DOS cannot browse here; the answer comes from local files.                                                                                                                                      confused clarify request ask one short question                                                                                                                 Clarify request                                                 Ask one short question.                                                                                                                                                                         talk open conversation dos                                                                                                                            